metadata.name: Nanoko Verse NFT
metadata.description: NANOKO is a collection of 7,777 unique handcrafted artworks crafted using the smart contract ERC-721T. Each one-of-a-kind artwork is actually hand-painted by a well-known artist and hits the market. It contains exclusive accessories that symbolize NANOKOVERSE. Dimensions: 3000x3000 px. https://www.nanokoverse.com/
